<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>File Sharing - Download Files</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f7ff;
            color: #333;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .animated-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: #1e3c72;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .ball {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.8;
            animation: float 6s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(0) scale(0.8);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-100px) scale(1.2);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateY(0) scale(0.8);
            }
        }

        .ball:nth-child(1) {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            animation-duration: 6s;
            animation-delay: 0s;
            top: 20%;
            left: 10%;
        }

        .ball:nth-child(2) {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            background-color: #00c4cc;
            animation-duration: 5s;
            animation-delay: 2s;
            top: 30%;
            left: 40%;
        }

        .ball:nth-child(3) {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: #6a89cc;
            animation-duration: 7s;
            animation-delay: 1s;
            top: 60%;
            left: 70%;
        }

        .ball:nth-child(4) {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background-color: #38ada9;
            animation-duration: 8s;
            animation-delay: 3s;
            top: 40%;
            left: 80%;
        }

        .ball:nth-child(5) {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: #1e90ff;
            animation-duration: 6.5s;
            animation-delay: 4s;
            top: 10%;
            left: 60%;
        }

        .content-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .heading {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .paragraph {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #fff;
            background: #007bff;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="animated-bg">
        <!-- Floating colored balls -->
        <div class="ball"></div>
        <div class="ball"></div>
        <div class="ball"></div>
        <div class="ball"></div>
        <div class="ball"></div>
    </div>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="content-box">
            <h1 class="heading">Files Shared With You</h1>
            <p class="paragraph">Someone has shared files with you through our secure platform. You can easily download
                the files below. Click the button to get started.</p>
            <a class="download-btn" href="<%= downloadLink %>">Download File</a>
            <p class="paragraph">If you encounter any issues with the download, feel free to reach out to our support
                team. We're here to assist you.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>